    <title>Flexible Workflow - Agent Determination Rule Failed</title>
    <updated>2025-02-21T10:58:57.310000+01:00</updated>
    <author>
      <name>StefanosRappos</name>
      <uri>https://community.sap.com/t5/user/viewprofilepage/user-id/1550570</uri>
    </author>
    <content>&lt;P&gt;Hello!&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;I have set up the flexible workflow scenario for Sales Orders and I want to use the team Functionality .&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;I set up the Teams and Responsibilities :&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="StefanosRappos_1-1740131305715.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/228490iCD5CCA3C08C4884D/image-size/medium/is-moderation-mode/true?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="StefanosRappos_1-1740131305715.png" alt="StefanosRappos_1-1740131305715.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;and the respective sales workflows&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="StefanosRappos_2-1740131375538.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/228491i5864934EDDDC433A/image-size/medium/is-moderation-mode/true?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="StefanosRappos_2-1740131375538.png" alt="StefanosRappos_2-1740131375538.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;My workflows are getting triggered ,but there's no agent determined.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;You can see the error below:&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="StefanosRappos_0-1740131192377.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/228489i9E408D3CDF95068B/image-size/medium/is-moderation-mode/true?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="StefanosRappos_0-1740131192377.png" alt="StefanosRappos_0-1740131192377.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;Now , it seemed strange to me that the system can't find the agent responsibility rule ,so I digged in and find the standard rule ID for the workflow template&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="StefanosRappos_3-1740131505650.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/228492iC7D374ACD1D3847C/image-size/medium/is-moderation-mode/true?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="StefanosRappos_3-1740131505650.png" alt="StefanosRappos_3-1740131505650.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;So , my guess is that this rule /FUNC/CMR1LVLA ,cannot be determined.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;I used the fiori apps "Manage Responsibility Rules" and "Manage Responsibility Context"&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;In the first one , there is no&amp;nbsp;/FUNC/CMR1LVLA in the list , which strikes me as unusual.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;Also in the second one , there is no agent rule assigned.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="StefanosRappos_4-1740131678995.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/228493i38CBA5C64254D8D2/image-size/medium/is-moderation-mode/true?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="StefanosRappos_4-1740131678995.png" alt="StefanosRappos_4-1740131678995.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;So , is there something missing?&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;I would expect to see the&amp;nbsp;/FUNC/CMR1LVLA in the Responsibility Rules and Assigned to WS02000006 in the Responsibility Context.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;Do I have to "install" these via a note or something?&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;Also , is there anything else I can check?&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;</content>
    <link href="https://community.sap.com/t5/technology-q-a/flexible-workflow-agent-determination-rule-failed/qaq-p/14023513"/>
    <published>2025-02-21T10:58:57.310000+01:00</published>
  </entry>
